      "content": "hey, ive been feeling kinda weird for the last hour. my chest feels heavy like there is something sitting on it and i feel really nauseous and just totally wiped out. i have been struggling with some bad anxiety lately so i was wondering if this could just be an anxiety attack or if i should be worried about something else?>",
