      "content": "wait, you're sure it's not a heart attack? i'm just really scared cause the pressure feels so real and the nausea is making me feel like i'm gonna throw up. i don't really want to go to the a&e if i don't have to, it's always such a huge ordeal. if i take the aspirin and do the walk like you said, it'll definitely settle down? i really think it's just the stress from work.",
